00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:04,620
 Ali bi definitivno rekla da trebamo

849
00:38:04,620 --> 00:38:07,140
 biti tanko čutni, osjetljivi

850
00:38:07,140 --> 00:38:09,920
 i evo, prvo srcem ljubiti osobu,

851
00:38:09,920 --> 00:38:11,620
 a onda sa njom razgovarati.

852
00:38:11,620 --> 00:38:13,260
 Rekla bi ono, kad pričamo iz srca,

853
00:38:13,260 --> 00:38:15,700
 kad pričamo iste natopljenosti,

854
00:38:15,700 --> 00:38:18,200
 kad nam Bog da kako da vidimo osobu,

855
00:38:18,200 --> 00:38:19,000
 kako da čujemo,

856
00:38:19,120 --> 00:38:20,520
 kad smo u tom duhu ljubavi,

857
00:38:20,520 --> 00:38:22,880
 onda su puno manje šanse

858
00:38:22,880 --> 00:38:24,740
 da ćemo pogriješiti u ovako nekim

859
00:38:24,740 --> 00:38:27,940
 povredama koje možemo napraviti

860
00:38:27,940 --> 00:38:29,020
 namjerno, nenamjerno.

861
00:38:29,020 --> 00:38:30,440
 Tako da bi rekla da treba biti

862
00:38:30,440 --> 00:38:32,880
 sa puno pažnje i poštovanja

863
00:38:32,880 --> 00:38:34,920
 prema tom procesu i prema osobi

864
00:38:34,920 --> 00:38:36,300
 i možda više ići na to

865
00:38:36,300 --> 00:38:37,820
 da čuješ kako je ona.

866
00:38:38,520 --> 00:38:40,680
 I da možda nemaš u sebi onako

867
00:38:40,680 --> 00:38:43,540
 joj, zašto ti nisi pokrenula šest godina,

868
00:38:43,540 --> 00:38:44,960
 što je bilo u mom slučaju,

869
00:38:44,960 --> 00:38:47,400
 nego, ej, šta ti se događalo do sad?

870
00:38:47,400 --> 00:38:49,660
 I možda ćeš onda čut nešto

871
00:38:49,660 --> 00:38:50,940
 što će u tebi razbiti

872
00:38:50,940 --> 00:38:52,500
 tu potencijalnu predrasudu.

873
00:38:52,500 --> 00:38:54,400
 Da, sam se samo trebala pokreniti,

874
00:38:54,400 --> 00:38:55,520
 da je to samo stvar,

875
00:38:55,520 --> 00:38:57,140
 volje, odluke,

876
00:38:57,140 --> 00:38:58,280
 kako nisi prije.

877
00:38:58,280 --> 00:39:00,720
 Mi nikad ne znamo nečiju patnju

878
00:39:00,720 --> 00:39:02,780
 i ono s čim se osoba bori.

879
00:39:03,220 --> 00:39:04,580
 Misliš da je to i dobar način

880
00:39:04,580 --> 00:39:07,040
 za pristupiti osobama oko nas

881
00:39:07,040 --> 00:39:08,000
 koje vidimo da se bore

882
00:39:08,000 --> 00:39:10,060
 s prekomjernom tjelesnom težinom.

883
00:39:10,060 --> 00:39:12,000
 Jednostavno biti tu, pitati

884
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:14,220
 ili jednostavno ništa sa strane,

885
00:39:14,220 --> 00:39:15,580
 moliti i čekati.

886
00:39:15,580 --> 00:39:17,240
 Misliš li da se treba umiješati

887
00:39:17,240 --> 00:39:19,340
 ako vidiš da neko ne poduzima,

888
00:39:19,340 --> 00:39:20,920
 a štetno utječe na njega?

889
00:39:20,920 --> 00:39:22,320
 Pa ja bi rekla, evo,

890
00:39:22,320 --> 00:39:23,500
 po svom iskustvu,

891
00:39:23,500 --> 00:39:24,580
 možda, ne znam sad,

892
00:39:24,580 --> 00:39:26,240
 ono, za sve situacije,

893
00:39:26,240 --> 00:39:28,400
 ono, šta bi nešto bilo ispravno,

894
00:39:28,400 --> 00:39:30,820
 to sad ovisi i kakva je osoba

895
00:39:30,820 --> 00:39:32,140
 i kakav im je odnos

896
00:39:32,140 --> 00:39:34,020
 s kojim je rekla bi stupan bliskosti

897
00:39:34,020 --> 00:39:35,920
 i ono, kako ja razgovaram,

898
00:39:35,920 --> 00:39:36,920
 ako sam ja, ono,

899
00:39:36,920 --> 00:39:39,480
 nekako ka osoba direktan

900
00:39:39,480 --> 00:39:41,420
 i možda ne pažljiviji u komunikaciji,

901
00:39:41,420 --> 00:39:42,460
 malo je dobro vidjeti,

902
00:39:42,460 --> 00:39:44,160
 ok, kako ću nešto reći na koji način,

903
00:39:44,160 --> 00:39:46,820
 ali znam da u mom konkretnom primjeru

904
00:39:46,820 --> 00:39:49,260
 za mene su stvarno bili blagostov ljudi

905
00:39:49,260 --> 00:39:50,500
 koji su mi dali do znanja,

906
00:39:50,500 --> 00:39:52,720
 ej, vidim da je nešto drugačije,

907
00:39:52,720 --> 00:39:54,680
 šta se događa, ono,

908
00:39:54,680 --> 00:39:56,580
 vidim da ovo nisi ti,

909
00:39:56,580 --> 00:39:58,360
 da ovo potpuno nisi ti.

910
00:39:58,360 --> 00:40:00,700
 I tako da rekla bi kad iz ljubavi

911
00:40:00,700 --> 00:40:01,660
 je došla ta briga,

912
00:40:01,660 --> 00:40:03,480
 ja sam osjetila u tome ljubav

913
00:40:03,480 --> 00:40:05,640
 i bilo mi nekako drago

914
00:40:05,640 --> 00:40:08,120
 da neko sa mnom vidi tu istinu

915
00:40:08,120 --> 00:40:09,960
 u kojoj je meni bilo teško pogledat.

916
00:40:09,960 --> 00:40:11,560
 Ali definitivno,

917
00:40:11,560 --> 00:40:12,680
 rekla bih da je to jedna

918
00:40:12,680 --> 00:40:14,020
 lijepa podrška,

919
00:40:14,020 --> 00:40:16,520
 ali ako vidimo da je nešto dugo

920
00:40:16,520 --> 00:40:17,880
 i ponavljajuće problem,

921
00:40:17,880 --> 00:40:20,760
 da je zbilja bolje sa stručnom osobom,

922
00:40:20,760 --> 00:40:22,640
 sad ovisno na koje razine

923
00:40:22,640 --> 00:40:23,900
 nam treba stručna podrška,

924
00:40:23,900 --> 00:40:25,780
 ali zbilja sa nekim kontinuirano

925
00:40:25,780 --> 00:40:27,540
 prolaziti taj put,

926
00:40:27,900 --> 00:40:29,880
 makar u početku dok tu neku

927
00:40:29,880 --> 00:40:32,240
 osjetljiviju djelnicu ne prođeš.

928
00:40:32,240 --> 00:40:35,440
 Vam osjeća da će ili sručna pomoć

929
00:40:35,440 --> 00:40:36,840
 ili podrška,

930
00:40:36,840 --> 00:40:38,820
 ili čak bilo kakva podrška,

931
00:40:38,820 --> 00:40:40,000
 jer vidim često...

932
00:40:40,000 --> 00:40:41,480
 Dakle, svijek je možda otišt na trening.

933
00:40:41,480 --> 00:40:43,680
 Ja sam imala jednu osobu

934
00:40:43,680 --> 00:40:44,940
 koja tad,

935
00:40:44,940 --> 00:40:46,680
 mislim, ona je ovako direktnija,

936
00:40:46,680 --> 00:40:47,240
 ali u ljubavi,

937
00:40:47,240 --> 00:40:47,800
 ona me reka,

938
00:40:47,800 --> 00:40:49,320
 gle, ovako ne ide,

939
00:40:49,320 --> 00:40:50,940
 ja ću s tobom i šetat na jarun.

940
00:40:50,940 --> 00:40:52,400
 Reci mi vrijeme.

941
00:40:52,400 --> 00:40:54,240
 I to je meni bilo super.

942
00:40:54,240 --> 00:40:55,560
 Ajme, neko je spreman

943
00:40:55,560 --> 00:40:57,020
 id sa mnom šetat na jarun.

944
00:40:57,020 --> 00:40:58,600
 Druga osoba je bila spremna

945
00:40:58,600 --> 00:40:59,560
 id sa mnom trenirat.

946
00:40:59,560 --> 00:41:00,800
 To su bili ono...

947
00:41:00,800 --> 00:41:01,100
 To baš znači.

948
00:41:01,100 --> 00:41:02,040
 Konkretni...

949
00:41:02,040 --> 00:41:03,900
 Možemo uves podijela milo srđo.

950
00:41:03,900 --> 00:41:05,560
 Da, da, to baš znači.

951
00:41:05,560 --> 00:41:06,140
 Super.

952
00:41:06,600 --> 00:41:08,780
 I isto tako, možda,

953
00:41:08,780 --> 00:41:10,280
 evo još kao jedan primjer,

954
00:41:10,280 --> 00:41:12,600
 kada sam ja se odlučila

955
00:41:12,600 --> 00:41:13,880
 nakon te malo pauze

956
00:41:13,880 --> 00:41:15,200
 javiti ovom drugom trenuru

957
00:41:15,200 --> 00:41:15,860
 gdje sam sada,

958
00:41:15,860 --> 00:41:18,280
 dogodio mi se zdravstveni problem

959
00:41:18,280 --> 00:41:19,920
 koji me objektivno spričavao

960
00:41:19,920 --> 00:41:21,840
 i koji nikako nije prolazio,

961
00:41:21,840 --> 00:41:22,960
 koji je na kraju ispao jedan

962
00:41:22,960 --> 00:41:24,920
 ono psihosomatizam,

963
00:41:24,920 --> 00:41:26,360
 jel, u biti da je to bila

964
00:41:26,360 --> 00:41:28,060
 reakcija psiher.

965
00:41:28,060 --> 00:41:29,700
 Ja sam sad jedan brinut o sebi

966
00:41:29,700 --> 00:41:31,240
 i to dijelo je jako opasno

967
00:41:31,240 --> 00:41:32,860
 i onda je tijelo imalo svoju reakciju

968
00:41:32,860 --> 00:41:34,500
 i to nije prolazilo određeno vrijeme.

969
00:41:35,480 --> 00:41:36,480
 I nazvala sam osobu

970
00:41:36,480 --> 00:41:37,540
 koja me, ono, kažem,

971
00:41:37,540 --> 00:41:39,260
 zna 14 godina,

972
00:41:39,260 --> 00:41:40,140
 prostudirala me

973
00:41:40,140 --> 00:41:42,320
 i rekao sam da taj dio,

974
00:41:42,320 --> 00:41:43,220
 gle, ja sad želim,

975
00:41:43,220 --> 00:41:45,600
 ali ja sad objektivno ne mogu više,

976
00:41:45,600 --> 00:41:46,780
 nije moj izgovor razlog,

977
00:41:46,780 --> 00:41:47,600
 nego, evo.

978
00:41:47,600 --> 00:41:48,260
 Stvarno, da.

979
00:41:48,260 --> 00:41:49,700
 Da, i on kaže,

980
00:41:49,700 --> 00:41:50,720
 odi tamo,

981
00:41:50,720 --> 00:41:52,500
 makar prstić trenirala,

982
00:41:52,500 --> 00:41:54,240
 makar odi tamo,

983
00:41:54,240 --> 00:41:56,160
 znači samo se pojavi na to mjestu.

984
00:41:56,160 --> 00:41:58,400
 i ja sam se onda stvarno javila

985
00:41:58,400 --> 00:42:00,120
 i dogovorila prvi termin

986
00:42:00,120 --> 00:42:01,040
 koji je bio, evo,

987
00:42:01,040 --> 00:42:01,760
 petog trećeg,

988
00:42:01,760 --> 00:42:03,780
 znači prije godinu i devet mjeseci

989
00:42:03,780 --> 00:42:05,620
 i otprilike.

990
00:42:05,620 --> 00:42:08,040
 I dan prije sam bila na misi

991
00:42:08,040 --> 00:42:10,280
 i baš sam prikazala taj dio

992
00:42:10,280 --> 00:42:11,700
 i sa zravljem i sa tijelom,

993
00:42:11,700 --> 00:42:12,820
 ono, Bože, evo,

994
00:42:12,820 --> 00:42:13,460
 molim te,

995
00:42:13,460 --> 00:42:14,800
 daj mi svoju milost da mogu.

996
00:42:15,160 --> 00:42:17,260
 i pod mislom sam baš osjetila,

997
00:42:17,260 --> 00:42:19,600
 ono, od sutra kreće tvoje zravljenje

998
00:42:19,600 --> 00:42:20,660
 i stvarno ti simptomi,

999
00:42:20,660 --> 00:42:21,820
 kad sam otišla na trening,

1000
00:42:21,820 --> 00:42:25,220
 u roku dva, tri dana su se potpuno povukli.

1001
00:42:25,220 --> 00:42:26,200
 Čeo, veće, da.

1002
00:42:26,200 --> 00:42:28,100
 Mislim, to je malo ekstremni primjer,

1003
00:42:28,100 --> 00:42:30,180
 može bolje ići ovim naravnim putem,

1004
00:42:30,180 --> 00:42:33,260
 ali, evo, u mojej situaciji je bilo tako.

1005
00:42:33,260 --> 00:42:36,900
 Imam osjećaj da nas puno ljudi koči,

1006
00:42:36,900 --> 00:42:38,900
 u bilo kakvoj nekakvoj disciplini

1007
00:42:38,900 --> 00:42:39,800
 ili na ovoj navici,

1008
00:42:39,800 --> 00:42:42,260
 to što...

1009
00:42:42,260 --> 00:42:43,960
 Perfekcionizam.

1010
00:42:44,640 --> 00:42:45,580
 To što bismo, ono, kao,

1011
00:42:45,580 --> 00:42:46,700
 ako smo full u tome,

1012
00:42:46,700 --> 00:42:47,660
 onda idem.

1013
00:42:47,660 --> 00:42:50,560
 Ali ako to znači da sam nalila,

1014
00:42:50,560 --> 00:42:51,640
 onda neću uopće.

1015
00:42:51,640 --> 00:42:53,720
 Ja vidim to sebi ponekad,

1016
00:42:53,720 --> 00:42:54,560
 aha, ovoj tjedan,

1017
00:42:54,560 --> 00:42:55,520
 znači, meni je kao,

1018
00:42:55,520 --> 00:42:57,340
 može, redovito treniram,

1019
00:42:57,340 --> 00:42:59,580
 ako treniram bar dva dana u tjednu.

1020
00:42:59,580 --> 00:43:01,460
 I onda znam točno kad mi ovako gužva

1021
00:43:01,460 --> 00:43:02,600
 neka na poslu ili nešto

1022
00:43:02,600 --> 00:43:03,440
 i vidim kao,

1023
00:43:03,440 --> 00:43:04,760
 nema šanse, neću možu cijeliti,

1024
00:43:04,760 --> 00:43:06,540
 je pun mi raspred, možda, petak,

1025
00:43:06,540 --> 00:43:07,400
 ma neću ni petak.

1026
00:43:07,400 --> 00:43:08,620
 Ma, ono, kao, ako neću,

1027
00:43:08,620 --> 00:43:09,600
 da će mi taj jedan ako,

1028
00:43:09,600 --> 00:43:11,060
 a zapravo, ili ono,

1029
00:43:11,060 --> 00:43:11,900
 bolje je da,

1030
00:43:11,900 --> 00:43:13,320
 neću uopće trenirati,

1031
00:43:13,320 --> 00:43:14,580
 a realno bolje je da,

1032
00:43:14,580 --> 00:43:14,960
 ne znam,

1033
00:43:14,960 --> 00:43:16,800
 napravim deset čučnjeva doma

1034
00:43:16,800 --> 00:43:18,260
 ili petnest minuta šetnje,

1035
00:43:18,260 --> 00:43:18,620
 ili,

1036
00:43:18,620 --> 00:43:19,720
 ma bilo što,

1037
00:43:19,720 --> 00:43:20,780
 da se samo protegnem

1038
00:43:20,780 --> 00:43:21,940
 je opet bolje od ništa.

1039
00:43:22,200 --> 00:43:23,320
 I to je jedan faktor

1040
00:43:23,320 --> 00:43:25,860
 kako ljudi često pristupaju promjeni,

1041
00:43:25,860 --> 00:43:26,560
 ono što vidim,

1042
00:43:26,560 --> 00:43:28,440
 bilo kad neko ovako sa mnom

1043
00:43:28,440 --> 00:43:29,540
 podijeli privatno,

1044
00:43:29,540 --> 00:43:30,680
 jer ga taj put inspirira,

1045
00:43:30,680 --> 00:43:31,600
 pa želi podijeliti

1046
00:43:31,600 --> 00:43:32,600
 svoj način promjene,

1047
00:43:32,600 --> 00:43:35,140
 ili u mentoriranju ljudi,

1048
00:43:35,140 --> 00:43:36,140
 to poimanje,

1049
00:43:36,140 --> 00:43:37,420
 ono, sve ili ništa

1050
00:43:37,420 --> 00:43:39,220
 i kako ta promjena treba izgledati

1051
00:43:39,220 --> 00:43:40,740
 i koliko treba biti savršena,

1052
00:43:40,740 --> 00:43:42,460
 a mi sebi ne možemo

1053
00:43:42,460 --> 00:43:44,460
 zagarantirati potpunu dosjednost

1054
00:43:44,460 --> 00:43:45,200
 i to je onaj dio

1055
00:43:45,200 --> 00:43:46,600
 nesavršeno kretanja

1056
00:43:46,600 --> 00:43:48,180
 i bolje je

1057
00:43:48,180 --> 00:43:49,860
 u nekim dijelovima

1058
00:43:49,860 --> 00:43:50,980
 biti nesavršen,

1059
00:43:51,100 --> 00:43:52,780
 ali biti dugoročan,

1060
00:43:52,780 --> 00:43:54,800
 jer ta promjena treba biti održiva.

1061
00:43:54,800 --> 00:43:56,740
 Mi se ne možemo izolirati

1062
00:43:56,740 --> 00:43:59,700
 da imamo potpuno savršene uvjete.

1063
00:43:59,700 --> 00:44:01,060
 Imaćemo posao,

1064
00:44:01,060 --> 00:44:03,720
 imaćemo neku emocijalnu težinu,

1065
00:44:03,720 --> 00:44:05,220
 s nekim ćemo se posvađati,

1066
00:44:05,220 --> 00:44:08,440
 prolazit ćemo možda neke konflikte

1067
00:44:08,440 --> 00:44:09,880
 na poslu privatnu,

1068
00:44:09,880 --> 00:44:10,220
 ne znam,

1069
00:44:10,220 --> 00:44:12,280
 šta god je nekome križ,

1070
00:44:12,280 --> 00:44:13,620
 ne znam, bilo šta,

1071
00:44:13,620 --> 00:44:16,200
 ali ok, šta je ono što je meni moguće?

1072
00:44:16,200 --> 00:44:20,100
 I imam taj neki maksimalan plan,

1073
00:44:20,200 --> 00:44:21,100
 dajmo tako nazvati,

1074
00:44:21,100 --> 00:44:23,040
 da su sve okolnosti dobre.

1075
00:44:23,040 --> 00:44:25,560
 Ali ne u ime toga propustiti,

1076
00:44:25,560 --> 00:44:27,400
 ok, što mi je sad moguće u ovom trenutku

1077
00:44:27,400 --> 00:44:28,540
 i sve se to zbraja.

1078
00:44:28,540 --> 00:44:30,840
 Evo, to je ono što je zapravo radosna vijest.

1079
00:44:30,840 --> 00:44:33,320
 Ovisno da li ne idemo ili idemo,

1080
00:44:33,320 --> 00:44:35,540
 ali radosna je vijest da se sve zbraja.

1081
00:44:35,540 --> 00:44:36,780
 I da ti mali koraci

1082
00:44:36,780 --> 00:44:38,540
 pomiću velike planine.

1083
00:44:38,660 --> 00:44:42,580
 Tako da ta srpljivost i dosjednost su baš jako važne.

1084
00:44:42,580 --> 00:44:45,820
 I perfekcionizam zbilja mnoge koći

1085
00:44:45,820 --> 00:44:47,300
 i mene je bio koćio.

1086
00:44:47,300 --> 00:44:49,660
 I jednostavno sam morala prihvatiti,

1087
00:44:49,660 --> 00:44:52,280
 ako ću ja očekivati te parametre,

1088
00:44:52,280 --> 00:44:54,440
 doslovno nikad neću krenuti.

1089
00:44:54,440 --> 00:44:56,120
 Ni u poduzetništvo,

1090
00:44:56,120 --> 00:44:57,740
 ni u odnos prema sebi kroz navike.

1091
00:44:58,220 --> 00:44:59,720
 Idem s onim što imam

1092
00:44:59,720 --> 00:45:02,460
 i gledat ću da imam maksimalno volju

1093
00:45:02,460 --> 00:45:04,780
 da s parametrima kojim imam resursima

1094
00:45:04,780 --> 00:45:06,720
 u datom trenutku činim najbolje.

1095
00:45:06,720 --> 00:45:10,580
 Meni uvijek kad se borim s tim skriptom savršenosti

1096
00:45:10,580 --> 00:45:13,000
 pomaže ono kao samo baci misao,

1097
00:45:13,000 --> 00:45:14,540
 samo baci dravo u vatru.

1098
00:45:14,540 --> 00:45:16,940
 Čeko imaš tu vatru samo ju treba održavati.

1099
00:45:16,940 --> 00:45:19,720
 Nekad će to biti balvan koji će gore dva dana,

1100
00:45:19,720 --> 00:45:21,040
 a nekad će to biti čačkalica

1101
00:45:21,040 --> 00:45:24,080
 koja će čisto eto ostaviti neki mali žar

1102
00:45:24,080 --> 00:45:25,100
 da može nastaviti dalje.

1103
00:45:25,420 --> 00:45:28,920
 Ali vrijedi samo nastaviti se kretati što kašiš.

1104
00:45:28,920 --> 00:45:31,800
 Baš lijepa i motivirajuća priča Anđela

1105
00:45:31,800 --> 00:45:33,800
 i vjerujem da ne samo s ovom pričom

1106
00:45:33,800 --> 00:45:35,740
 oko težine, već generalno

1107
00:45:35,740 --> 00:45:37,460
 za promjenu nekog načina razmišljenja

1108
00:45:37,460 --> 00:45:38,980
 i uvoženja dobrih navika,

1109
00:45:38,980 --> 00:45:42,180
 vraćanja discipline, tako da hvala ti na tome.

1110
00:45:42,180 --> 00:45:44,060
 Hvala tebe. Rekla bih da je zapravo

1111
00:45:44,060 --> 00:45:45,660
 ovo zajednički nazivnik

1112
00:45:45,660 --> 00:45:47,340
 semu ovome jedna metanoa.

1113
00:45:47,340 --> 00:45:52,120
 Srca, uma, tijela, duha, svakodnevice.

1114
00:45:52,120 --> 00:45:53,740
 Ne zanimariti nijedan dio.

1115
00:45:54,380 --> 00:45:55,780
 ima li neka poruka

1116
00:45:55,780 --> 00:45:57,800
 koju želiš prenijeti našim ženama

1117
00:45:57,800 --> 00:45:59,620
 koje nas prate, možda i muškarcima?

1118
00:45:59,620 --> 00:46:01,580
 Ne nužno samo onima

1119
00:46:01,580 --> 00:46:04,280
 koji se možda bore s prekomjernom tijelesnom težinom,

1120
00:46:04,280 --> 00:46:05,740
 već i generalno ovim temama

1121
00:46:05,740 --> 00:46:06,560
 koje smo pokrili.

1122
00:46:07,400 --> 00:46:09,900
 Pa rekla bih, evo, nemoj sebi stat na putu

1123
00:46:09,900 --> 00:46:12,660
 i za ono što ti se čini nemoguće,

1124
00:46:12,660 --> 00:46:15,000
 evo, povjeri Bogu da ti da milost,

1125
00:46:15,000 --> 00:46:17,180
 da na onaj put koji je dosjedan,

1126
00:46:17,180 --> 00:46:20,560
 nesavršen, nekad padneš, nekad se ustaneš,

1127
00:46:20,560 --> 00:46:23,500
 ali da, evo, da ne ostaneš sebi i dužan sebe.

1128
00:46:24,500 --> 00:46:25,820
 Lijepo si to završila.

1129
00:46:25,820 --> 00:46:27,780
 Hvala ti puno još jednom na dolasku

1130
00:46:27,780 --> 00:46:29,080
 i nadam se da se opet čujemo,

1131
00:46:29,080 --> 00:46:30,780
 vidimo u nekom podcastu.

1132
00:46:30,780 --> 00:46:31,940
 Možda, radujem se.

1133
00:46:31,940 --> 00:46:33,440
 Sretno dalje s tvojom disciplinom.

1134
00:46:33,440 --> 00:46:34,180
 Hvala ti.

1135
00:46:34,180 --> 00:46:34,960
 Hvala tebi.

1136
00:46:34,960 --> 00:46:37,500
 Drage naše osnažene, osnaženi,

1137
00:46:37,500 --> 00:46:38,620
 lijepo vas pozdravljamo

1138
00:46:38,620 --> 00:46:40,300
 na naše sljedeće zanimljive teme.

